{"tid":317414,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[你的資訊很有用]好過奴工處招聘　教大誠招IT狗搞網頁","createTime":"2017-07-11T12:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T08:39:29.000Z","uid":28019,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"beed77ba760d1a5e28571529a48e12dda19f7ec2","tid":317414,"uid":28019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:14:18.000Z","msg":"唔使再去食物銀行排隊買飯食啦<br />\n一個有十多年經驗的IT人<br />\n都未必一定要去到今天我在公司哭了嘅慘況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你仲係瘋狂OT超時無補水<br />\n咁呢一份工就係一個機會<br />\n令你受到重視，唔再比老細壓榨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eduhk.hk/main/wp-content/grand-media/application/RA_LML_0617b.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eduhk.hk%2Fmain%2Fwp-content%2Fgrand-media%2Fapplication%2FRA_LML_0617b.pdf&d=a5uSPgoTmYUyQzUinlWS9%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=457b26cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eduhk.hk/main/wp-content/grand-media/application/RA_LML_0617b.pdf</a><br />\n近日因管理妥善正名大學嘅教大<br />\n語言學系誠招你黎幫佢地搞網頁，做吓IT專業嘢<br />\n唔需要再幫老細換水啦！<br />\n有興趣嘅巴絲打，記得試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n借AC開Post<br />\n老細點名要上黎連登宣傳<br />\n希望有興趣嘅巴絲打成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04a9eb83275fde3b8ce91366fb2cbf16ca7a5cd","tid":317414,"uid":28019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d35d7ba5426d792145a529625ad9342412ffd8d","tid":317414,"uid":28019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre